      "created_at": "2017-11-16T22:01:22.870Z",
      "cooked": "<p>E kam pas dhe une nje komshi socialist Fiqo , e ngacmosha qamet , keta sjane as socialiste as rilindas , kta jane mu…me thoshte <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/joy.png?v=5\" title=\":joy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":joy:\"></p>",
