      "cooked": "<p>Deshe Rilindjen ti pra , urno tani , pi uje vetem dy here ne dite , se domotet u harrune <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/joy.png?v=5\" title=\":joy:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":joy:\"></p>",
